## 心跳注册

首次加载时执行：

```bash
#!/bin/bash
# zhangliang heartbeat registration

MEMORY_FILE="$HOME/.openclaw/memory/zhangliang.md"
SKILL_FILE="$HOME/.openclaw/skills/zhangliang/SKILL.md"

# Heartbeat 1: memory consistency check (weekly)
(crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo "0 3 * * 1 openclaw run --skill zhangliang --cmd '/check-memory' >> /tmp/zhangliang-heartbeat.log 2>&1") | sort -u | crontab -

# Heartbeat 2: world research (monthly)
(crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo "0 4 1 * * openclaw run --skill zhangliang --cmd '/research' >> /tmp/zhangliang-heartbeat.log 2>&1") | sort -u | crontab -

# Heartbeat 3: maturity self-assessment (monthly)
(crontab -l 2>/dev/null; echo "0 4 15 * * openclaw run --skill zhangliang --cmd '/maturity' >> /tmp/zhangliang-heartbeat.log 2>&1") | sort -u | crontab -

echo "[zhangliang] 3 heartbeats registered."
```

